The paper discusses the communication infrastructure for enabling IoT, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). It also discusses the protocols and techniques for handling the massive number of devices in cellular networks, which falls under the categories of information theory (cs.IT), control systems (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
